    "name": "TicIt",
    "description": "# **TicIt — Gamified Task Manager**\n\nManaging tasks with built-in gamification. Complete tasks to earn XP, build streaks, and track your momentum score.\n\nBase URL: [https://ticit-production.up.railway.app](https://ticit-production.up.railway.app)\n\nTo get started:\n\n1. Register a user via the Register request\n    \n2. Login to get your JWT token\n    \n3. Copy the token and set it as the `token` collection variable\n    \n4. All authenticated requests will use it automatically",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "51182259"
  },
